summary: This mod changes your game's font into the beautiful CatCafe, by designer Shara Weber.
descriptionHtml:
This mod changes your games font to the one on the picture:
[img]http://s12.postimg.org/69hc1h97h/20160925110420_1.jpg[/img]

[b]Install:

[/b]Install with your mod manager of choice.

[b]Compatability:[/b]

Compatable with any mod that does not change interface\fontconfig.txt; which is almost every mod on the Nexus. Only font mods do this.
author: SirSidney
